%% MyAIStorybook - System Sequence Diagram: Export Story to PDF Scenario

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant System as :System
    
    Note over User,System: Export Story to PDF Scenario (Main Success)<br/>System is treated as BLACK BOX
    
    User->>System: selectStory(story_id)
    System-->>User: story_details
    
    User->>System: requestPDFExport()
    System-->>User: export_started
    
    System-->>User: pdf_ready(file_path, download_url)
    
    User->>System: downloadPDF()
    System-->>User: pdf_file
    
    Note right of System: System generates PDF internally<br/>with story text and images<br/>Returns downloadable file
